query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS threat_intelligence (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  source ENUM('alienvault_otx', 'misp', 'manual') NOT NULL,
  indicator_type ENUM('ip', 'domain', 'url', 'hash', 'email') NOT NULL,
  indicator_value VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
  threat_level ENUM('low', 'medium', 'high', 'critical') NOT NULL,
  threat_type VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  confidence_score INT DEFAULT 50,
  first_seen TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  last_seen TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  tags TEXT,
  metadata TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_indicator (indicator_value),
  INDEX idx_source (source),
  INDEX idx_threat_level (threat_level)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS threat_feed_configs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  feed_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  feed_type ENUM('alienvault_otx', 'misp', 'custom') NOT NULL,
  feed_url VARCHAR(500),
  api_key VARCHAR(500),
  enabled INT DEFAULT 1 NOT NULL,
  sync_interval INT DEFAULT 3600,
  last_sync TIMESTAMP NULL,
  last_sync_status ENUM('success', 'failed', 'pending') DEFAULT 'pending',
  error_message TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
